data.description: $200k Loan assumption @ 3.5% and/or seller financing of $200k @ 4% interest. OR preferred lender will offer up to $5k in closing credits or buy downs. Spacious home with gorgeous views on over an acre! This home boasts 5 bed 3.5 baths with an open floor plan great for entertaining. New appliances (less than 1 year old) New Hot water heater, 3 car garage, built in fire pit, Play house in the back yard with power, tons of storage, partially finished basement. Wake up to deer and wild turkeys in your back yard in this quiet, friendly neighborhood. Fireplace is unfinished. All materials included with sale. All information deemed reliable but buyer or buyers agent to verify. Seller is a licensed real estate agent. Call today for more information or to schedule a showing.
